task.summary: Created the main menu screen with three buttons and background.

added game 1 score and total score to displayed on the game stats page. added two methods loadData() and saveData() in GameStats.java and MainActivity.java to be able to save any score for any game for any user.

added game 3 to be displayed in stats page and will now be used to calculate the total score. GameManager.java draw method for game2 now also dynamically changes message to show what is to be done next.
Added a register account functionality. Log in now only works if user has first registered his/her account. If log in has wrong credentials then a toast message is displayed.
